# Local search/compile caches — regenerated on demand
.zenwiki/search.db
.zenwiki/search.db-shm
.zenwiki/search.db-wal
.zenwiki/preflight.json
.zenwiki/dedup-audit.jsonl
.zenwiki/*.log

# IMPORTANT: .zenwiki/manifest.json IS tracked — it's the compile state
# the watcher needs across machines. Don't add .zenwiki/ wholesale.

# ─── Agent skills + permissions are product files ──────────────────
# Repo-root .gitignore ignores .claude/ for Claude Code's local state,
# but the skill bundle and permission allowlist live with the wiki and
# must be tracked. Same for the .agents/ symlink Codex reads.
!.claude/
!.claude/skills/
!.claude/skills/**
!.claude/settings.json
!.agents/
!.agents/skills
# Local-only Claude state stays ignored
.claude/settings.local.json
.claude/projects/
.claude/transcripts/
